{"tid":1754671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全港10個警察宿舍及其家人用票向林鄭表達要求《成立警暴獨立調查委員會》","createTime":"2019-11-25T09:34:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T11:17:41.000Z","uid":230104,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bb73c29ed699d6e3b32d99ded008d0e10a5c4b85","tid":1754671,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5xUXRFm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5xUXRFm.png&h=da83b119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聲討警暴成為今次區議會選舉的主題，而今次區選共涉及最少11個紀律部隊宿舍選區，除有包括順利紀律部隊宿舍的觀塘「雙順」外，其餘有紀律部隊的選區均全數由民主派當選，這個結果似乎反映在警暴下，選區內即使有紀律隊部隊宿舍，也不足以拖累民主派得票。"},{"pid":"81b9e077f47df46518bc2389977899608e40d8cf","tid":1754671,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:34:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">依家我哋區選贏咗，外國好關注我哋！<br />\n係咪連少少嘢都唔肯做呀？</span><br />\n<br />\n最新的tweets 一定響bot <br />\n總之<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> Retweet Like Reply </span></span>就得<br />\n㩒入👉 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=9a77f2bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task</span></span> 攞任務<br />\n<br />\nSen. Marco Rubio<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1198773889112956928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1198773889112956928&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=3e1109fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1198773889112956928&h=2dc87735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1198773889112956928</a><br />\n<br />\nSen. Rick Scott<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1198739997911846913\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1198739997911846913&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=7a4acc29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1198739997911846913&h=291b9b3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1198739997911846913</a><br />\n<br />\nSen. Marsha Blackburn<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1198773803976810496\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1198773803976810496&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=18321d00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1198773803976810496&h=03c18e02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1198773803976810496</a><br />\n<br />\n更加多嘅tweet請入bot搵<br />\n<br />\n（twitter戰線)國際都關注今次香港的區選<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754022</a>"},{"pid":"2d7b5cce1b508a17918239b8ba3b4fb8cd7160de","tid":1754671,"uid":230104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:35:40.000Z","msg":"在觀塘雙順選區，坐擁全港最大型的紀律部隊宿舍，前警務人員陳祖光、建制派創建力量的符碧珍參選，但兩人相爭未有令民主派當選，民協梁漢祺最終敗選，得票率只有36.8%，但陳祖光亦沒有在此大型宿舍中佔優，只有949票。符以51.5%得票率取勝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他有警察或者紀律部隊的宿舍，完全無助建制派選情。所有在涉及有紀律部隊或者警察宿舍的選區，無論民主派是爭取連任、或者首次挑戰的民主派，全部也獲勝。<br />\n<br />\n曾經爆發大型衝突的黃大仙紀律部隊宿舍，位於黃大仙選區「龍趣」，也是由民主派莊鼎威勝出。莊奪得2,911票，以260票的差距，力壓爭取連任的李東江的2,651票。"},{"pid":"81a189854a25ca529f84df3c7d3f756d5c7f17f1","tid":1754671,"uid":230104,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:37:26.000Z","msg":"有合理理由相信，呢6個月嚟濫捕、知法犯法、違規違法既警察集中住喺順利宿舍度"},{"pid":"27403b1d37c2f3fcc29a351cf1686f109ee299a5","tid":1754671,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:42:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2774de291dc3d9b9fc7f1e04fa665637ab9c1a02","tid":1754671,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:48:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a14bb41f49332385b4d96167642e124616c4ebbc","tid":1754671,"uid":19437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:51:42.000Z","msg":"一定有好多警二代手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f29e7dd254f2030288ddc3927051d3265bfb84e","tid":1754671,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a14bb41f49332385b4d96167642e124616c4ebbc","tid":1754671,"uid":19437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:51:42.000Z","msg":"一定有好多警二代手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"紀律部隊都有好多唔係警察?"},{"pid":"8fb64b51af43d864dfcd13f61d63a37950e663ca","tid":1754671,"uid":200328,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"81a189854a25ca529f84df3c7d3f756d5c7f17f1","tid":1754671,"uid":230104,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:37:26.000Z","msg":"有合理理由相信，呢6個月嚟濫捕、知法犯法、違規違法既警察集中住喺順利宿舍度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:02:21.000Z","msg":"OK<br />\n燒狗宿就燒觀塘呢到<br />\n有目標了"},{"pid":"953c2d72cfa0f16a5bbfb9d09a68f0bebb32d34c","tid":1754671,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:03:10.000Z","msg":"想查我？"},{"pid":"d2d36bc4b3d5d16e26de1a152278155fb85d1ffb","tid":1754671,"uid":33875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:03:39.000Z","msg":"白警嫂，白狗仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/smile_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb8d8e423e9da7b42ade9c18a2dbff859fe6baa","tid":1754671,"uid":226466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"953c2d72cfa0f16a5bbfb9d09a68f0bebb32d34c","tid":1754671,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:03:10.000Z","msg":